title: Bonus: How to UnFuck Your Brain LIVE
itunes:title: Bonus: How to UnFuck Your Brain LIVE
description:
In this bonus episode, I’m featuring a recent webinar I did on the 4 mindfucks of patriarchy and how they are holding women back from living an empowered life.

As women, we often feel anxious, insecure, guilty, or not good enough, even if our life looks good from the outside.

In this episode, we cover how social conditioning is creating these negative feelings and experiences, and how you can go about changing it.

If you want to liberate yourself from self-doubt, insecurity, anxiety, and fear, visit UnFckyourbrain.com/join to learn more about the UnF*ck Your Brain program.
